race.comment: WILLOW'S WITCH (1) has a terrific record here with two wins and two placings from four starts. Recorded a 0.8 lengths win (21.77) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Expected to be in the finish. FEDERAL ICEMAN (4) is a progressive dog who scored his 5th career win last time at this track, scoring by 2.25 lengths (21.67). Got the money at his only try from this box. One of the prime contenders. FLAMING COMET (2) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the money last time though when second (21.88) at this track. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Winning chance. GIFTED LILLY (8) has claims fresh from a recent placing at big odds.
